{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249060/extras/tallygif.gif?t=1729002361\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tombstone Tally</strong> is somewhere between bingo and a Scavenger Hunt, where you search a graveyard for tombstones that match up with squares on your card. Play with your friends and beat them in hunting down the many different possible features of the graves!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TALLY 'ROUND THE CLOCK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play during the day, at night, in blackout mode, with or without AI groundskeepers around, or with infinite shovels to send your friends flying over and over! Careful though, it's pretty addicting to give someone a good shovel smack, you might never finish the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249060/extras/banner1.png?t=1729002361\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VISIT THE LOVELY ARENA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you want something faster pace, try the Arena map! In this smaller map with it's own fast paced mode, be the first to find 5 graves that match the current wave's stipulation. Everyone is searching at the same time, so if They're close to winning do your best to send them tumbling off the edge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249060/extras/banner2.png?t=1729002361\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BEAT UP THE BOTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you just want to kill some time, jump into single player and play against the AI! They'll take you on in the graveyard or in the arena. Maybe even turn on infinite shovels and don't stop running while you try to win!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Tally!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamco